      "title": "BASL voices concern over 22A",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Bar Association of Sri Lanka has expressed concern over the 22nd Amendment to the Constitution.",
        "\u201cIt is our view that the bill in its present form will not create the climate of confidence which is necessary,\u201d said President of the Bar Association of Sri Lanka, Saliya Peiris PC on Friday (8)."
      ],
